@apiUrl =  http://localhost:8080/items/rum/


###Get all rooms

GET {{apiUrl}}

###Get one product

GET {{apiUrl}}

### Create new product
POST {{apiUrl}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "number" : 4,
  "persons" : 4,
  "name" : "Deluxe room"
}


### Update Product info
##Uppdatera hela dataobjekt
PUT {{apiUrl}}/1001
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name" : "Shirt",
  "price" : 29
}


### Update Product info
##Patch kan uppdatera enskilda fält
PATCH {{apiUrl}}/1001
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name" : "Jeans",
  "price" : 29
}




###Delete product
DELETE {{apiUrl}}/1004